### ============================================================
### 25. Data Ingestion
### ============================================================

### Create pipeline
POST {{host}}/api/doclib/ingestion/pipelines
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "SWIFT Message Ingestion",
  "source_type": "financial",
  "source_config": {"endpoint": "sftp://swift.bank.com/mt103", "format": "swift_mt103"},
  "transforms": [
    {"operation": "set_classification", "config": {"level": "confidential"}},
    {"operation": "add_tag", "config": {"tag": "swift_mt103"}}
  ],
  "schedule": "0 */4 * * *",
  "enabled": true
}

### List pipelines
GET {{host}}/api/doclib/ingestion/pipelines
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get pipeline
GET {{host}}/api/doclib/ingestion/pipelines/{{pipelineID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Run pipeline
POST {{host}}/api/doclib/ingestion/pipelines/{{pipelineID}}/run
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List runs
GET {{host}}/api/doclib/ingestion/runs?pipeline_id={{pipelineID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Ingest record
POST {{host}}/api/doclib/ingestion/ingest
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "pipeline_id": "{{pipelineID}}",
  "title": "SWIFT MT103 - WT-2026-03-16-001",
  "content": "Sender: HSBCGB2L\nReceiver: BOFAUS3N\nAmount: USD 450,000.00",
  "doc_type": "transaction_record",
  "classification": "confidential",
  "tags": ["swift_mt103", "wire_transfer"],
  "metadata": {"sender_bic": "HSBCGB2L", "amount": "450000"}
}

### Delete pipeline
DELETE {{host}}/api/doclib/ingestion/pipelines/{{pipelineID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

